I got my 32qt Winware stockpot on Friday and am almost ready to brew my first 5gal batch! (boiing water in it to build up the oxidation layer now)seriously though, how goddamned long does it take to boil 5 gal of water on a domestic gas stove? I think it's been at least 30 minutes at this point. . . thank god I have access to a propane burner!sadly I haven't devoted the funds to a chiller at this point, so I think I'll be chilling my first batch in the bathtub. . .
